<paragraph id="F446D301E753593797B32B4CFD8AF871" blockId="3.[151,1436,1915,2019]" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">
<emphasis id="C68D0F13E753593797B32B4CFECFF807" bold="true" box="[151,312,1915,1941]" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">Diagnosis:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="33F9A882E7535937961D2B4BFD9FF807" authorityName="C. D. Tyrrell &amp; L. G. Clark" authorityYear="2013" box="[313,616,1916,1941]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Rhipidocladum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cordatum">
<emphasis id="C68D0F13E7535937961D2B4BFD9FF807" box="[313,616,1916,1941]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">Rhipidocladum cordatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="33F9A882E7535937942D2B4BFC36F807" authorityName="McClure" authorityYear="1973" baseAuthorityName="Parodi" baseAuthorityYear="1944" box="[777,961,1916,1941]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Rhipidocladum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="harmonicum">
<emphasis id="C68D0F13E7535937942D2B4BFC36F807" box="[777,961,1916,1941]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">R. harmonicum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by its cordate culm leaf blades, greater number (70–100) of branchlets per node, greater number of florets (9–10) per spikelet, and more closely (
<quantity id="33017EE4E7535937924A2B95FF31F871" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" unit="mm" value="6.5" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="4.0">4–9 mm</quantity>
) spaced spikelets per synflorescence.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
